To install this library do:

>> make 

to compile the code. Default behaviour is that the library is installed in lib folder.

>> make install

to install the libraries and header files in the path specified by PREFIX variable.
The value of this variable can be changed from inside the Makefile.

>> make remove 

to uninstall the installed things

>> make clean

to remove the binaries and object and shared files.

***************
The header files contains proper usage of each function.